Package rl.photoviewer.model

Contains classes to create the model component of the photo viewer.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IndexedGeoPoint
    Interface for ordered latitude longitude pairs.
    MapData
    Abstraction of the MapDataManager which focuses on read access methods.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExifDataManager
    Tool for collecting EXIF metadata for all photos in a directory.
    GeoRefPoint
    Relates a point defined by image coordinates to a point defined by geographical lat-lon coordinates.
    KeywordExpression
    Represents a propositional sentence to control visibility of photos marked with keywords.
    MapDataManager
    The MapDataManager maintains all the data which is needed for map display and position marking.
    MapDataManager.MapParams  
    PhotoExporter
    Provides methods to copy and rename files.
    PhotoMetadata
    Container for selected Exif metadata.
    PhotoMetadata.SortByDateComparator
    Compares photo dates (Exif) if available.
    PhotoMetadata.SortByFileNameComparator
    Compares the file names.
    PVModel
    Facade which provides access to the complete state of the photo viewer.

Package rl.photoviewer.model Description

Contains classes to create the model component of the photo viewer. The main class is PVModel. It implements a facade for the component. Model and view are only allowed to access the model using the facade.
Author:
Ruediger Lunde
